[SN]TITLE[SN]
Fugitive child rapist arrested in Brazil

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A child rapist who fled the UK has been arrested in Brazil after three years on the run.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Portuguese national Antonio Pedro De Olivera Alves, 44, was convicted in his absence at Stafford Crown Court of raping the 12-year-old girl.
He was sentenced to an 11-year jail term in 2013, and a warrant for his arrest was issued.
Alves, who was arrested in South America earlier this month, will face extradition proceedings, police said.
